FLYING INTO 2023 LIKE...PEACE OUT 2022!
.
As I reflect on this last year,  I can not help but smile in awe of the magic of 2022. I entered this year thinking it would be just another mundane year,  but it turned out to be a wonderful year of self growth and success.  God surrounded me with the most amazing, talented and bold humans and the mental shift that this provided was truly priceless, in every way.  I'm taking this mindset into 2023 and bringing whomever is up for the ride, along with me...we are setting massive goals and conquering big dreams! Cheers to 2023!
.

Counting my blessings as we start this year off with a whirlwind @xfl/@gstq tour!  Orlando-Vegas-Arlington-LA-NYC-Arlington-LA....let's do this!
.
This flight had me all up in my feelings!  Four years ago, almost to this very day, when the rug was pulled out from under me and  unexpectedly, my career came screeching to a halt, I honestly felt as though I would never fully recover....I couldn't have dreamt, in my wildest of dreams, of being where I am today! It took me 4 years to do it, but surrounded by amazing people who inspire me, trust me and fully believe in me...your girl is back and thriving!  Life is wild y'all!  This is your reminder that even when you feel like things aren't going your way, God always has a bigger plan for you. You just need to surrender your fears and disappointment and have faith. A sling shot must be pulled back to rocket forward!
